uws-server README file

----------
Files in this directory
----------

* README
This file...

* hello_bottle.py
first bottle application based on tutorial

* uws_server.py
The UWS server as a bottle app

* uws_server.wsgi
config for Apache WSGI app

* uws_server_debug.log
log for uws_server app

* uws_db.sql
defines a basic DB for uws_server

* libs/
bottle library, can also be installed in python directly
select the right import command

* views/
templates for bottle

----------
To install
----------

sudo pip install bottle
sudo pip install bottle-pgsql


